{"tid":2418441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英外相：香 港 人 權 遭 有 系 統 地 侵 犯","createTime":"2021-02-22T15:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:27:04.000Z","uid":227801,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18d9037ebcf030982e9199f862f2794f39b38f55","tid":2418441,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XodddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=a15dc096\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&h=cc35c813\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%AD%E6%9C%89%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%B0%E4%BE%B5%E7%8A%AF-%E4%BF%83%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E5%85%AC%E6%AD%A3%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/</a><br />\n英國外相藍韜文在英國時間周一（22 日）的聯合國人權理事會高級別會議上，就香港及新疆人權問題發言。藍韜文在會上提及，香港人的權利被侵犯，要求在港舉行自由公正的立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n據《路透社》報道，英國外相藍韜文在會上發表預錄講話，在提及香港政治局勢時，形容香港人的權利及自由，被「有系統地侵犯（Systematically Violated）」，而由中國對港實施的《港區國安法》更遏制港人的自由，要求香港當局舉行自由、公正的立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在會上提及新疆人權問題，表明新疆維族人權現況是「不能接受的（Beyond the pale）」，又形容中方對新疆維吾爾族人施以大規模、極端的行為，包括酷刑、強迫勞動和婦女絕育等。<br />\n<br />\n促聯合國派員調查新疆<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在會上要求聯合國派出聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特（Michelle Bachelet），或一位獨立的專家，調查新疆人權狀況，並強調有關調查須賦予專家「緊急及不受限制進入新疆（Urgent and unfettered access）」的權利。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文辦公室較早時曾表示，藍韜文會譴責聯合國人權理事會成員國，中國及俄羅斯的人權紀錄，亦對緬甸及白羅斯的政治局勢表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n另外，藍韜文早前經視象會議出席保守黨華人之友 (Conservative Friends of the Chinese) 活動時，同樣提及就香港議題，稱曾對中國政府提出訪問行程，以尋求合作機會，「我曾提出到訪北京、及與我的同行中國外長王毅對話」，唯中方至今仍未同意相關安排。"},{"pid":"5b41f7c2a574145fc6d8cbb5d93f976d689d49e5","tid":2418441,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a623ebfa5ce3b32ae9c1d8a904ad428aa90cef","tid":2418441,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab2fdbd47e04edeabf3cdadf70a0d841076625","tid":2418441,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"講啲我唔知嘅嘢得唔得？"}]}